Name: Super Orbit
About the game: Danger lurks in the stars. Jump past obstacles to reach your place in the universe. Unlock new lifeforms and explore new heights. Addictive one button platforming - Jump as high as you can while avoiding various obstacles. Unlock new characters - Collect coins and unlock all the lifeforms. Beat your friends' high score - Compete on the leaderboards to get the highest score.
